We are one of the most popular courses in South Florida, and we offer year-round access to our 18-hole course for locals and visitors worldwide. Our facilities include a small driving range, putting green, ProShop, and restaurant Apocalypse BBQ. At Killian Greens, we are committed to providing exceptional customer service, which is why we have consistently been rated as one of the highest-quality golf courses in South Florida. We take pride in offering a world-class golfing experience to all who visit us. Book online here

Membership
Killian Greens Golf Club offers a Golf Membership that grants full access to our Golf Course, Pro Shop, and Restaurant. Memberships are available to everyone, including non golfers. Our Membership is dedicated to making you feel welcome and enhance your Golf Club experience. We look forward to having you join the Killian Greens Golf Club family. Below you will see everything our Membership has to offer.

Membership Rules & Regulations
On the day of play, members shall register (check-in) themselves and any guest prior to using the Club Facilities. Tee times must include names of all players in the group.
Memberships are individual and non-transferable, which is associated with the privately owned and operated Killian Greens Golf Club.
Appropriate attire is recommended at all times on the Golf Course, Pro Shop, and Restaurant. Collared Shirts required.
State liquor laws prohibit any individual from bringing alcoholic beverages on the Club’s property. Personal coolers are not permitted on the Club premises unless for verifiable medical reasons.
The Club is not an insurer of the property of Members or their guests. Insurance of Member and guest property is the responsibility of each Member. The Club will not be responsible for the loss or damage to any property however caused, regardless of where the property is checked, kept, left or stored on the premises of the Club.
Members shall pay for any loss or damage to the Club property for which they or their guests are responsible.
All members have a responsibility to support the rules of golf and to assist in their observance by other members and guests.
A copy of the Membership / Golf Rules & Regulations are kept at the Pro Shop, please ask a staff member if you’d like to have one
